  "description": "A nighttime view of a long bridge stretching across dark water, likely a bay or sea. The bridge is illuminated with a string of orange lights that create a bright, linear path. In the foreground, dark silhouettes of trees frame the scene, creating a natural border. The sky is a deep, dark blue, almost black, emphasizing the contrast with the bridge lights. A pale, crescent moon is visible in the upper right corner. The water surface appears calm, reflecting some of the lights. The overall composition gives a sense of distance and tranquility.",
